==English==

===Adjective===

'''nonconformist'''
# Someone who does not [[conform]] to accepted [[belief]]s, [[custom]]s or [[practice]]s.
# {{christianity}} A member of a [[Protestant]] [[church]] which does not [[observe]] the [[doctrine]]s of the [[established]] church, especially of the [[Church of England]].

